description: Square array A(n>=0,k>=1) (listed antidiagonally: A(0,1)=1, A(1,1)=1, A(0,2)=1, A(2,1)=2, A(1,2)=1, A(0,3)=1, A(3,1)=3, ...) giving the number of n-edge general plane trees fixed by k-fold application of Catalan Automorphisms A057511/A057512 (Deep rotation of general parenthesizations/plane trees).
